        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "You can either change StatusLine to remove `reverse` (e.g: `au ColorScheme * hi StatusLine gui=NONE cterm=NONE` before sourcing your colorscheme), or add `nocombine` to your custom highlights (e.g: `hi ModeNormalColor guibg=#b8bb26 guifg=#303030 gui=bold,nocombine`).",
            "created_at": "2026-04-01T09:05:04Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/38670#issuecomment-4168636867",
